name: Ricky Iwasaki
title: Injineer Software
summary: Soo-saare Software khibrad u leh, raadinaya fursad cusub oo uu kaga shaqeeyo mashaariicda waaweyn. Waxaan xiisaynayaa abuurista ama ku darista koodka dadka kale si ay u isticmaalaan. Waxaan aaminsanahay in xirfadahaygu ay yar yihiin marka la barbardhigo internetka, sidaas darteed waxaan aad u xiiseynayaa la shaqeynta qalabka kale, adeegyada, luqadaha barnaamijyada.

experience.title: Injineer Software
responsibilities: La habeeyey oo la hirgeliyey codsiyada shabakadda ee la miisaami karo iyadoo la adeegsanayo React iyo Node.js
La kaashaday maamulayaasha alaabada si loo hagaajiyo shuruudaha loona hubiyo keenista waqtiga
APIs RESTful loo sameeyay oo la dayactiray ee codsiyada shabakada
Qoraallo la sameeyay si otomaatig loogu sameeyo hawlaha oo loo horumariyo hufnaanta

experience.title: Kaaliyaha Tababaraha Teniska
responsibilities: Barista farsamooyinka teniska ee koox koox ah oo ka kooban 5-10 ciyaartoy
Ka dhigista casharka mid madadaalo leh oo soo jiidasho leh ciyaartoyda
Isagoo ka mas'uul ah badbaadada ciyaartoyda maxkamadda, gaar ahaan ciyaartoyda da'da yar iyo kuwa ka weyn, sida 3 jir iyo 60 jir.

experience.title: Xiriiriyaha dibadda
responsibilities: Dib u soo celinta alaabta shelf
Ku rarida dalabaadka gawaarida xamuulka qaada
Ka caawinta macaamiisha inay alaab ka helaan dukaanka
U haynta jawi badbaado leh oo saaxiibtinimo leh macaamiisha iyo shaqaalaha
